{"tid":1211984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解唔試下幫佢地解除裝備，減輕負擔","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T17:06:18.000Z","uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"422f825fca460506827d29408567b00d2d7db991","tid":1211984,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:02:22.000Z","msg":"大熱天時，啲狗孭住咁重裝備跑成日咁辛苦，愛狗人仕點解唔幫下佢地減輕負擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日見到好多情況係幾隻狗衝過黎咬幾十人，<br />\n幾十人係咁走，<br />\n如果當時可以4,5人一組捉住啲狗仔，<br />\n唔使搶走佢啲野黎用，一剝落黎就周鳩圍掉，<br />\n然後散水，什至連啲狗仔衫都幫佢地除埋，<br />\n咁就唔會比狗咬得咁慘"},{"pid":"e3b4ae8207419bcde6883cba689d1ece39106f66","tid":1211984,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}